<subsection name="Generate Solr schema from PDS data dictionary" id="GenSchema">
<p>
To generate Solr schema from a PDS data dictionary, run <i>generate-solr-schema</i> command:
</p>
<p>
<source>
Usage: registry-manager generate-solr-schema &lt;options&gt;

Generate Solr schema from one or more PDS data dictionaries.

Required parameters:
  -config &lt;path&gt;  Configuration file.
Optional parameters:
  -outDir &lt;dir&gt;   Output directory for Solr schema file. Default value is '/tmp/registry'.
  -log &lt;file&gt;     Log file. Default is /tmp/registry/registry.log.
  -v &lt;level&gt;      Logger verbosity: 0=Debug, 1=Info (default), 2=Warning, 3=Error.
</source>

</p>
<p>
This command is described in <a href="reg-custom.html">Registry Customization</a> section.
</p>

</subsection>

