Update Solr schema from one or more PDS data dictionaries.

Required parameters:
  -config &lt;path&gt;      Configuration file.
Optional parameters:
  -solrUrl &lt;url&gt;      Solr URL. Default is http://localhost:8983/solr
  -zkHost &lt;host&gt;      ZooKeeper connection string, &lt;host:port&gt;[,&lt;host:port&gt;][/path]
                      For example, zk1:2181,zk2:2181,zk3:2181/solr
  -collection &lt;name&gt;  Solr collection name. Default value is 'registry'
  -log &lt;file&gt;         Log file. Default is /tmp/registry/registry.log.
  -v &lt;level&gt;          Logger verbosity: 0=Debug, 1=Info (default), 2=Warning, 3=Error.

</source>
</p>
<p>
This command is described in <a href="reg-custom.html">Registry Customization</a> section.
